name: Racing Skiff
Lore: 'Barada and Klaatu strip down and rebuild old skiffs to race on the Dune Sea. Jabba allows the practice to continue for now.',
Text: 'May deploy with a driver (must be Barada, Klaatu, or a non-unique alien) as a ''react''. May add 1 driver and 3 passengers. May move as a ''react''. If lost, any characters aboard may ''jump off'' (disembark).',
